episodes.title: Kenneth Copeland becomes Demon Possessed on stage.
episodes.description:
Watch as False Teacher Kenneth Copeland becomes demon possessed right on stage at a convention in Canada.
Before you comment read this:
If anyone speaks in a tongue, it should be by two or at the most three, and each in turn, and one must interpret;
— 1 Corinthians 14:27
Please refrain from using foul language in the comment section. We all agree that Copeland is creepy and sick. I would just ask to keep the language to a PG Rating...
Thank you.
